sql.statement: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS p90days ( _id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, track VARCHAR(50), dayname VARCHAR(50), dayID INTERGER, weeknumber INTERGER, daynumber INTERGER, type INTERGER, date VARCHAR(50), hasRipper INTERGER)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS results ( _id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, profile VARCHAR(50), ExerciseName VARCHAR(50), weight INTERGER, reps INTERGER, band VARCHAR(50), time VARCHAR(50), pullup VARCHAR(50), date VARCHAR(50), notes VARCHAR(100))
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS weighin ( _id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, profile VARCHAR(50), weight INTERGER, date VARCHAR(50))
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS programs ( _id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, name VARCHAR(50), program VARCHAR(50))
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS p90Exercises ( _id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, dayID INTEGER, day VARCHAR(50), name VARCHAR(50), exernum INTEGER, type INTEGER)
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS userstats ( _id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, username VARCHAR(50), exername VARCHAR(50), weight INTERGER, reps INTERGER, time INTERGER, date INTERGER)
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS p90dayKey ( _id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, dayName VARCHAR(50), dayID INTERGER)
